            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Chicago</placeName>
                <date>June the 24<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1857</date>
            </p>
            <p><sic><addressee>Rev. I. Lesser</addressee></sic> Editor of the Occident in<lb/>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Gentleman!</p>
            <p>You will <sic>recieved</sic> hereby a <sic>copie</sic> from her<lb/> a
                    <sic>Newes</sic> Paper which was copied from the<lb/> Deborah published in
                    <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>, about<lb/> jewes=humboy ceremony of an
                dedication<lb/> of a new Grave=yard. which I would request<lb/> your honour to give
                a space in your paper<lb/> for the good of the Israelites in general.<lb/> I remain
                your very respectfully</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">J. C.</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p><sic><addressee>Rev. I. Lesser</addressee></sic>, Editor of the</p>
